Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.12,0:00:02.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,諸葛孔明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.68,0:00:05.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,家喻戶曉的三國時代天才軍師
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.39,0:00:08.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,孔明隨劉備一同
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.11,0:00:10.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,追逐天下太平的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.14,0:00:12.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,贏下了一場又一場激戰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.96,0:00:14.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但是在公元234年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.92,0:00:18.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,於五丈原 出師未捷身先死
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.65,0:00:21.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這是人們的普遍看法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.29,0:00:22.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不過孔明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.61,0:00:25.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在現代日本的澀谷重生了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.78,0:00:28.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,萬聖節快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.48,0:00:30.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這裡就是地獄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.26,0:00:32.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在狂歡的澀谷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.79,0:00:34.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,孔明遇上一位歌姬
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.54,0:00:39.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,聽了三次美妙的歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.34,0:00:41.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.87,0:00:44.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我已經想放棄當歌手了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.26,0:00:47.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,說實話 我覺得是時候放棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.39,0:00:50.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,天才軍師諸葛孔明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.44,0:00:51.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為了月見英子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.17,0:00:54.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,做出了重大決定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.39,0:01:06.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,CHANCE×CHANCE
