Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.67,0:01:15.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,HIGH Chitty Chitty Bang Bang
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.51,0:01:17.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,哀！？Chitty Chitty CHANCE CHANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.37,0:01:19.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,嗚呼！Chitty Chitty Bang Bang
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.26,0:01:20.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,愛！！Choki Choki Bang Bang
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.06,0:01:23.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,無論張三李四
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.20,0:01:27.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,全都心血來潮 好難受
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.45,0:01:30.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,龍舌蘭喝到醉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.00,0:01:34.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不存在的妄想連連 閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.72,0:01:39.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,夢是潘多拉 讓人想要打開
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.19,0:01:42.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,大家都期待著派對咖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.26,0:01:46.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,今晚不知道 爬不爬富士山
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.67,0:01:49.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,決戰是週末的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.43,0:01:51.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,CHANCE×CHANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.20,0:01:53.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,逢！！Chitty Chitty Bang Bang
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.45,0:01:57.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,別裝模作樣 好好享受 今晚嗨起來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.90,0:01:58.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,CHANCE×CHANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.65,0:02:00.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,哀！？Chitty Chitty Bang Bang
