Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.45,0:02:06.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,CHANCE×CHANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.20,0:02:08.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,嗚呼！Chitty Chitty Bang Bang
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.50,0:02:12.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,愚蠢的人更該HIGH 完美社會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.90,0:02:13.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,CHANCE×CHANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.66,0:02:15.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,愛！！Choki Choki Bang Bang
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.94,0:02:20.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,大家都是明日的超級明星 今晚一起派對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.88,0:02:28.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（孔明 施展計謀）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.22,0:02:30.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（孔明 施展計謀）\N本週的精選歌手開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.41,0:02:31.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（孔明 施展計謀）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.09,0:02:33.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那麼 這週的精選歌手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.53,0:02:35.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是謎團多多的偶像 AZALEA
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.87,0:02:37.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,今天將向大家全方位介紹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.81,0:02:39.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,她可愛且激情的魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.84,0:03:08.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我要成為你的軍師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.87,0:03:10.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你隨時可以向我下令
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.02,0:03:14.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我願貢獻綿薄之力 為你出謀劃策
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.96,0:03:17.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,話說我才不會下令呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.72,0:03:19.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,話說軍師是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.99,0:03:22.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,軍師 軍師…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.08,0:03:26.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,指的是為將領制定戰術的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.47,0:03:27.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,戰術是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.75,0:03:32.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,英子的夢想是出道？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.06,0:03:34.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還是吸引一萬名觀眾？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.30,0:03:39.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我的夢想嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.12,0:03:40.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（我是英子。在澀谷俱樂部BB演出中！）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.16,0:03:41.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（粉絲 208）\N好少
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.09,0:03:46.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好想讓更多人聽聽我的歌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.56,0:03:48.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.63,0:03:53.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,比如參加比利時舉辦的全球最大音樂節 Voiceleland\N（※ 源自比利時的音樂節「Tomorrowland」）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.87,0:03:56.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,粉絲才208人 根本是做夢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.52,0:04:00.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,或是參加日本最大規模的音樂節 SUMMER SONIA\N（※ 源自日本的音樂節「SUMMER SONIC」）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.43,0:04:03.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不管參加什麼 才208個粉絲肯定辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.97,0:04:08.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不行 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.33,0:04:10.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我都決定了 要再努努力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.69,0:04:12.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,現在就做好力所能及的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.68,0:04:14.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,千里之行始於五十步 一百步
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.93,0:04:17.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,孔明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.04,0:04:19.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,聽說你要當英子的經紀人 是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.99,0:04:21.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,請稱我為軍師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.93,0:04:23.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我可不會給你開工資
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.58,0:04:24.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.82,0:04:27.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,金錢本來就是次要的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.04,0:04:30.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你這人真的有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.91,0:04:32.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不敢當
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.31,0:04:33.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.42,0:04:35.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你託我找的東西到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.62,0:04:36.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.69,0:04:39.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,今天在「Z2O」舉辦的活動的門票
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.87,0:04:41.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你要兩張是準備跟英子一起去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.19,0:04:43.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.13,0:04:47.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我想要活躍於都內近郊的歌手情報
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:49.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,準備跟英子去偵查
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.85,0:04:53.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,非常感激 我就收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.06,0:04:56.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,剛才那下好讚 有家臣的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:04:59.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我是打工的 老闆你是雇主
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.06,0:05:03.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,理應盡到家臣的禮數
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.51,0:05:06.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,感覺你隨時有可能用計謀啊 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:10.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,如今已無敵人 計謀純屬紙上談兵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.74,0:05:12.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只要你一聲令下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.13,0:05:15.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我可以算個看透宇宙深淵的卦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.93,0:05:19.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,等到有需要的時候 再麻煩你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.41,0:05:21.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,嗯 等到有需要的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.81,0:05:29.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,說起來 孔明用過的計謀數不勝數
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.36,0:05:31.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,關於石兵八陣 你是怎麼看的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:34.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,石兵八陣是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.38,0:05:36.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,誒…就是那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.69,0:05:38.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,孔明的主君劉備
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.81,0:05:42.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,-被吳國武將陸遜追殺 命懸一線時 -站住
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.41,0:05:44.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,料到劉備會輸的孔明
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.79,0:05:47.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,將陸遜的軍隊引誘進石陣中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.27,0:05:48.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不出所料
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.98,0:05:54.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,使用幻術 將陸遜的士兵困在石陣中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.48,0:05:58.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,啊 那是這樣流傳的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.48,0:06:00.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,當故事看固然有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.73,0:06:02.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不過有點不現實啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.47,0:06:05.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,確實 好像是誇張了一點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.12,0:06:07.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只要利用好地形 氣象
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.70,0:06:09.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,看穿人的心理
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.56,0:06:10.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就可以辦到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.69,0:06:19.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,英子 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.56,0:06:23.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你是不打算換掉這身了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.45,0:06:24.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那就出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.25,0:06:26.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,去偵查
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.06,0:06:27.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,別喊出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.54,0:06:31.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,來來來 儘管檢查吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.04,0:06:35.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,感覺可以用來管理士兵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.18,0:06:38.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,把你手上那輕飄飄的東西放進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.62,0:06:41.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這相當於我身體的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.44,0:06:42.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,隨你便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.93,0:06:48.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.02,0:06:48.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（演唱會巡演 正在售票）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.29,0:06:50.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（演唱會巡演 正在售票）\N米亞·西表嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.44,0:06:50.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（演唱會巡演 正在售票）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.83,0:06:52.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（演唱會巡演 正在售票）\N這次活動的招牌歌手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.87,0:06:55.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（演唱會巡演 正在售票）\N換成軍隊 就相當於將領吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.99,0:06:59.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（演唱會巡演 正在售票）\N即蜀軍中的關羽張飛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.04,0:07:01.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這是米亞的Pinsta
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.31,0:07:02.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.92,0:07:06.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Pinsta的粉絲有10萬人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.10,0:07:07.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,年齡26歲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.23,0:07:11.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,魅力是渾厚的歌聲和人生信念
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.74,0:07:13.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.41,0:07:17.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你都徹底迷上音樂了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.00,0:07:18.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,來我的世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.87,0:07:33.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,下一個出場的就是米亞哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.19,0:07:34.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,第四位出場啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.87,0:07:38.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那肯定要在觀眾最興奮時出場啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.26,0:07:39.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,米亞人氣很高的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.87,0:07:41.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我還是第一次在現場看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.82,0:07:43.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,下面是大家期待已久的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.98,0:07:46.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,俱樂部活動中必不可少的超人氣歌手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.02,0:07:49.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,米亞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.25,0:07:58.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,If you play a game　
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.48,0:08:04.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,You give me the pain I don't know how much I mean to you baby
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.60,0:08:05.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna blame
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.95,0:08:07.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,You make me insane　
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.32,0:08:11.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Anyhow show me that your love is real
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.13,0:08:12.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,You say "I love you"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.73,0:08:13.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,唱功真好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.04,0:08:16.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是個存在感很強的歌手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.25,0:08:18.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一上來就唱這首歌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.26,0:08:21.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,翻唱經典歌曲可是很難的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.67,0:08:25.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,話說英子 BPM會不會太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.00,0:08:29.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,感覺這樣沒有維持住前面的節奏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.89,0:08:33.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,俱樂部活動每次都一定有當天的節奏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.32,0:08:36.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,於是要故意先抑後揚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.26,0:08:38.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,原來如此 先抑後揚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.78,0:08:41.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就能一口氣炒熱氣氛 中間不會減速啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.44,0:08:42.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,對對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.79,0:08:44.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可是為什麼要選在這時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.10,0:08:47.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,上一個歌手都炒熱氣氛了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.87,0:08:50.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,太浪費了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.76,0:08:52.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真是個麻煩的節目
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.27,0:08:56.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為什麼不能唱我自己的歌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.21,0:08:58.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,主辦者這是在跟我作對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.05,0:09:01.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,演出費也算不上豐厚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.12,0:09:04.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要不是經紀人哭著求我 我才不會來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.67,0:09:07.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,BPM一降臉都青了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.02,0:09:12.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,畢竟是你讓我隨心所欲發揮嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.12,0:09:21.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,曲調變了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.73,0:09:23.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,開場時降低的BPM又快起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.24,0:09:25.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為防觀眾感到乏味
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.73,0:09:28.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,中途讓舞者加入 自己也一起跳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.36,0:09:32.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,再加上紮實的唱功
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.76,0:09:40.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不知不覺間 觀眾的情緒都被帶動起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.90,0:09:42.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,米亞·西表
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.78,0:09:45.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,難怪如此有人氣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.35,0:09:48.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不過 帶動情緒的能力還是不如英子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.04,0:09:50.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,究竟是米亞有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.75,0:09:54.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還是我對她的歌聲不來電
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.95,0:09:58.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,音樂這東西還真深奧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.13,0:10:00.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我說孔明 你在念叨什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.57,0:10:01.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,來 拿上這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.92,0:10:02.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.92,0:10:05.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,分析就太不解風情了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.50,0:10:10.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,現在就享受音樂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.42,0:10:16.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好開心啊 米亞果然好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.17,0:10:18.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是啊 她是怎樣一個人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.12,0:10:21.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不清楚 應該是好人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.33,0:10:22.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.62,0:10:24.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.62,0:10:26.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,誒？去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.10,0:10:30.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.30,0:10:32.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.96,0:10:35.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我是米亞的粉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.08,0:10:39.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,此次前來 是為了說幾句鼓勵的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.13,0:10:42.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,米亞 有個說是你粉絲的Coser來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.74,0:10:43.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.61,0:10:49.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,找我有什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.88,0:10:52.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,您剛才引爆全場 讓我無比感動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.70,0:10:55.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,特前來向您表達我的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.75,0:10:59.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,米亞小姐的歌超好聽的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.48,0:11:00.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.38,0:11:02.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我…我也在當歌手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.58,0:11:04.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,雖然還是業餘的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.04,0:11:06.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不過經常在BB俱樂部唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.19,0:11:08.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,哦？你也是歌手嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.96,0:11:09.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.95,0:11:11.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你叫什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.02,0:11:11.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,英子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.99,0:11:15.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,歌手名是羅馬字 EIKO
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.47,0:11:20.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.15,0:11:22.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.20,0:11:24.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,米亞小姐問我名字了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.50,0:11:28.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,英子的魅力足以讓陰天放晴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.99,0:11:30.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我認為這是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.54,0:11:32.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真討厭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.35,0:11:33.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我說你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.74,0:11:35.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這週五有空嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.79,0:11:38.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在我參加的活動中出場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.08,0:11:40.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.03,0:11:43.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,嗯 詳情我私信發給你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.85,0:11:45.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,太感謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.69,0:11:48.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,然後 這是你的經紀人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.89,0:11:50.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,用Cosplay吸引眼球
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.97,0:11:52.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這戰術不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.24,0:11:55.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒 不是這樣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.41,0:11:56.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那就再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.97,0:12:02.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,孔明 老闆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.48,0:12:04.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,米亞給我發消息了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.91,0:12:07.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,說是要我在「LADYS READY NIGHT」出場
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.64,0:12:10.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,穿越俱樂部的活動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.55,0:12:12.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是個不小的舞台哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.22,0:12:14.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,從沒收到過這麼好的邀約 我好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.95,0:12:17.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,感覺我的運勢終於來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.26,0:12:19.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這時間表是認真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.14,0:12:22.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你後面是米亞·西表哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.63,0:12:25.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,誒？跟米亞同時出場？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.11,0:12:27.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.16,0:12:32.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,孔明 英子被當成墊背的了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.62,0:12:34.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,嗯 看來是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.08,0:12:38.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,米亞小姐這麼做肯定是給我機會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.15,0:12:41.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,看我有沒有能力在同一時間吸引觀眾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.37,0:12:42.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,英子…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.92,0:12:45.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,孔明 這是個機會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.45,0:12:48.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可以視為千載難逢的好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.55,0:12:50.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就…就是說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.57,0:12:53.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,於是 只要你一聲令下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.13,0:12:57.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我孔明縱使粉身碎骨也在所不辭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.04,0:13:00.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.72,0:13:02.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,軍師孔明 我命令你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.75,0:13:06.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,確保演出當天 我的舞池座無虛席
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.71,0:13:07.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,說笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.15,0:13:12.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為將之人 須占盡天時地利人和
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.73,0:13:16.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,勝利自當水到渠成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.09,0:13:19.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這句話我等很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.00,0:13:22.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,看來以軍師的身份行動的時刻到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.87,0:13:26.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我說的命令 姑且算是玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.74,0:13:29.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,派對咖孔明
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.96,0:13:35.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,英子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.78,0:13:38.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在營業前練習唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.87,0:13:40.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.34,0:13:41.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,謝謝 孔明
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.24,0:13:44.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.54,0:13:48.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你很擔心吧 怕吸引不到觀眾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.12,0:13:51.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,能不能別猜測別人的心思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.41,0:13:55.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,演唱活動 「LADYS READY NIGHT」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.53,0:13:57.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,活動設有三個舞池
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.86,0:14:00.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,觀眾可以自由往來於舞池之間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.80,0:14:04.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,能同時觀看多位歌手 形式著實有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.46,0:14:05.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但弊端是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:08.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,人們更偏向於聚集在人氣歌手的舞池
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.98,0:14:12.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我唱歌的時候肯定沒人來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.38,0:14:13.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我本以為是機會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.78,0:14:15.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這下沒信心了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.39,0:14:18.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,米亞·西表
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.80,0:14:20.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有很多忠實粉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.50,0:14:22.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有一定的動員力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.05,0:14:25.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,英子的舞池會無比冷清
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.52,0:14:27.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,米亞的舞池則會熱鬧非凡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.21,0:14:31.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,米亞恐怕是想利用籍籍無名的英子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:35.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,襯托自己舞台的盛況吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.79,0:14:37.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,方法還不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.89,0:14:41.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但在我看來純屬幼稚的下策
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.30,0:14:43.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,出現了 突然就得意起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.46,0:14:46.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（我一定會好好表演的！）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.54,0:14:47.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（我很期待 加油！）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.54,0:14:48.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（謝謝鼓勵（感激流涕））
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.07,0:14:51.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,米亞 我已經按照你的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.95,0:14:55.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,安排那個新人在週末的活動中出場了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.83,0:14:58.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,啊？新人？誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.40,0:14:59.88,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這就忘了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.20,0:15:02.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,跟個奇怪的男Coser一起來後台的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.51,0:15:03.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,粉絲才200人的歌手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.78,0:15:05.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,啊 那人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.50,0:15:06.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我都搞忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.62,0:15:07.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,幹得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.57,0:15:09.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這年頭實力是次要的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.07,0:15:11.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要的是自我包裝能力和感染力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.34,0:15:13.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,觀眾會聚集在你的舞池
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.62,0:15:15.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真狠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.37,0:15:18.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你說實力怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.82,0:15:22.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你實力也在她之上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.50,0:15:23.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,廢話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.85,0:15:29.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,別總健身 玩Pinsta
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.45,0:15:31.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,倒是練練唱功啊 練唱功
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.33,0:15:36.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,孔明 英子狀態怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.65,0:15:38.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,看起來幹勁十足
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.92,0:15:40.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,現在也在練習哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:41.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.35,0:15:45.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這是你要的穿越俱樂部的準確結構圖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.30,0:15:47.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.72,0:15:50.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,穿越有老闆熟人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.71,0:15:51.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.85,0:15:52.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,耳朵湊過來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.52,0:16:11.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不好 根本沒觀眾來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.97,0:16:14.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Pinsta之類的宣傳倒是挺努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.00,0:16:17.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,孔明也不知道上哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.14,0:16:19.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,開始緊張了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:20.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,英子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.24,0:16:22.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,該你出場了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.32,0:16:23.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.76,0:16:24.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.80,0:16:26.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只能上了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:27.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,盡全力唱歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.97,0:16:32.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,LADYS READY NIGHT 音量13
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.45,0:16:33.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,下一位登台的是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.95,0:16:36.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,米亞·西表
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.65,0:16:42.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好 嗨起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.94,0:16:47.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,1 2 1 2 3 4
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.35,0:16:48.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不愧是米亞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.25,0:16:51.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,吸引觀眾的能力不是一般強
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.57,0:16:52.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,英子的演出呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.95,0:16:57.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,果然觀眾基本都去米亞的舞池了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.78,0:17:00.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,孔明的計謀能奏效嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.13,0:17:02.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,來來來 這邊請
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.38,0:17:06.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在這邊請大家喝一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.33,0:17:09.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,孔明 這是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.09,0:17:12.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想靠酒釣觀眾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.36,0:17:13.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這就是你的計謀？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.50,0:17:16.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只要聽到英子唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.42,0:17:18.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,確實應該有人願意留下來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.84,0:17:21.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,喂 趕緊回米亞的舞池吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.03,0:17:23.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,說實話 這計謀太愚蠢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.35,0:17:25.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我太傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.53,0:17:28.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,竟然期待他能想出比肩真孔明的計謀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.75,0:17:31.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,被酒釣來的人怎麼可能指望得上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.81,0:17:35.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這類人只會跟風
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.38,0:17:37.88,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,咦？樓梯不在這邊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.88,0:17:40.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這不是廁所嗎 真逗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.00,0:17:42.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 兄弟姐妹們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.32,0:17:45.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,盡情嗨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.01,0:17:46.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,來點噪音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.70,0:17:49.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.08,0:17:50.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只要聽過我的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.71,0:17:52.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,今晚一定會很美妙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.67,0:17:53.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我說你們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:57.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,今天能來澀谷 能來這裡太幸運了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.33,0:18:00.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.44,0:18:03.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要是害得英子失去自信該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.54,0:18:04.88,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,孔明那混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.88,0:18:06.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,結束後看我怎麼收拾你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.41,0:18:08.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,咦？怎麼又是廁所？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.45,0:18:09.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真逗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.38,0:18:10.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,樓梯不見了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.79,0:18:13.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,話說 怎麼能錯過那場演出
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.31,0:18:14.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,-怎麼回事 -去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.24,0:18:15.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（We feel the heatbeat）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.70,0:18:17.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（We feel the heatbeat）\N這…這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.06,0:18:17.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（We feel the heatbeat）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.70,0:18:18.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（We feel the heatbeat）\N觀眾怎麼這麼多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.44,0:18:19.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（摘掉手錶吧）\N觀眾怎麼這麼多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.69,0:18:22.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（摘掉手錶吧）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.09,0:18:23.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（I sing a song for you）\N不行了 超開心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.67,0:18:24.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（Party at it's peak）\N不行了 超開心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.69,0:18:25.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（Party at it's peak）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.09,0:18:25.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（Party at it's peak）\N大家都在聽我唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.48,0:18:27.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（我要讓你如夢似幻）\N大家都在聽我唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.84,0:18:28.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（我要讓你如夢似幻）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.86,0:18:31.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（不嗨起來多無聊）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.91,0:18:35.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（你就在我眼前）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.67,0:18:37.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（我只想盡全力表達）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.02,0:18:38.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（我只想盡全力表達）\N好熱鬧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.50,0:18:38.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,唱歌那人是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.81,0:18:39.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（展現一切 show you my soul）\N唱歌那人是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.94,0:18:42.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（展現一切 show you my soul）\N這就是孔明的計謀？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.00,0:18:42.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（展現一切 show you my soul）\N究竟有什麼玄機
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.98,0:18:43.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,究竟有什麼玄機
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.22,0:18:44.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,看來成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.96,0:18:45.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,孔明
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.47,0:18:48.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,大家都留在舞池不肯走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.50,0:18:49.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你幹了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.53,0:18:51.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不是不肯走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.21,0:18:53.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,而是走不了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.84,0:18:54.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.64,0:18:56.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我來解釋一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.35,0:18:58.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我在舞池內釋放了大量煙霧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.65,0:19:00.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,讓觀眾的行動路線上的燈閃爍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.85,0:19:02.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,以降低判斷力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.81,0:19:04.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,讓著裝一樣的兩個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.61,0:19:07.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,按固定時間前往入口 廁所和員工出入口
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.93,0:19:08.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,擾亂觀眾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.93,0:19:11.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,另外還專門設置了兩個吧檯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.53,0:19:13.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,按正三角形擺放的樹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.16,0:19:15.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,作用相當於戰場上的軍旗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.68,0:19:18.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但由於間距相等 反而容易讓人迷惑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.36,0:19:22.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,而這個舞池是舞台在中心的鍋爐房構造
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.47,0:19:24.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,360度無死角 在哪都可以觀看演出
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.83,0:19:26.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,如此一來會怎樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.01,0:19:29.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒錯 觀眾無法抵達出口
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.25,0:19:32.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只能繞舞池一圈 最終抵達廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.50,0:19:33.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.52,0:19:35.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這麼狹小的舞池也能迷路？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.68,0:19:36.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,請看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.17,0:19:38.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,她們很費解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.84,0:19:39.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,奇怪 出口不是在這邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.15,0:19:40.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,-彷彿在不知不覺間被誘導至廁所了 -奇怪 出口不是在這邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.97,0:19:42.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,-彷彿在不知不覺間被誘導至廁所了 -可這裡不是廁所嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.00,0:19:44.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.59,0:19:45.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,純屬偶然吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.30,0:19:50.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,精通三國志的老闆應該知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.91,0:19:52.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這個計謀叫什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.43,0:19:54.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,難道說是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.88,0:19:56.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,石兵八陣？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.06,0:20:01.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一旦進入就再也出不去的必殺陣法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.86,0:20:04.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,難道他在這舞池重現了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.74,0:20:07.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,雖說這陣法不適合狹小空間
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.44,0:20:09.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但只要利用這個時代的器材
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.25,0:20:10.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就能輕易實現
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.14,0:20:12.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,出入口和廁所的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.92,0:20:15.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,也運用了風水力學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.78,0:20:19.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,孔明 你小子…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.41,0:20:21.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,希望你別誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.06,0:20:24.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,阻止觀眾離開的人的確是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.73,0:20:28.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但他們不願離開的真正理由是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.64,0:20:41.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,英子的歌的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.48,0:20:46.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.24,0:20:48.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我的舞池空蕩蕩的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.21,0:20:49.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,雜魚的舞池卻全是人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.75,0:20:51.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那個穿得很搞笑的經紀人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.98,0:20:53.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,把觀眾全帶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.83,0:20:57.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那你去把觀眾帶回來不就得了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.50,0:20:59.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,英子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.28,0:21:01.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.00,0:21:01.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.71,0:21:03.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,英子的Pinsta
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.17,0:21:05.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你關注上 給我盯緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.08,0:21:06.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為什麼要我來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.06,0:21:08.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這是經紀人失職吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.20,0:21:09.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,給我彌補失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.99,0:21:11.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我去健個身再回去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.07,0:21:14.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,練練唱功啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.29,0:21:16.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,今天的活動誰表現最好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.94,0:21:18.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,EIKO吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.02,0:21:19.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,觀眾也是最多的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.82,0:21:22.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真心可愛 歌唱得也好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.14,0:21:23.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,超懂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.04,0:21:29.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Hey DJ 躁起來 yeah yeah yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.97,0:21:31.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,來段心情上好↑↑的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.94,0:21:35.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,針丟地上 音樂響起 派對之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.75,0:21:39.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,喝吧 來 來 來 大家一起跳！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.60,0:21:41.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Hip-Pop People
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.09,0:21:45.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,撥打那奇蹟Number
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.65,0:21:53.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Yo！在這時代分享的MUSIC
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.00,0:21:54.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想將其找出 轉動地球儀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.99,0:21:58.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,生活動盪不穩 所以要重視平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.77,0:22:01.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,生活並非全是好事 所以「還能拼！」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.14,0:22:02.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,踢開糟糕的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.66,0:22:04.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,按下重啟的按鈕！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.54,0:22:06.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,DJ 音樂響起來！！此刻TRIP
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.10,0:22:10.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,跟隨前沿的節奏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.31,0:22:15.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,用心感受 搖擺起來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.03,0:22:19.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Hey DJ 躁起來 yeah yeah yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.94,0:22:21.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,來段心情上好↑↑的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.85,0:22:25.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,乘著浪 全力跳躍 舞蹈之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.68,0:22:29.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,喝吧 來 來 來 大家一起跳！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.50,0:22:31.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Hip-Pop People
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.01,0:22:36.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,直至天亮 奇蹟Number
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.05,0:22:43.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Hey DJ 躁起來 yeah yeah yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.84,0:22:46.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,喝吧 來 來 來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.75,0:22:50.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Hey DJ 躁起來 yeah yeah yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.99,0:23:01.88,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,英子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.71,0:23:04.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是不是累壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.03,0:23:06.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.42,0:23:08.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一晚上粉絲就過千了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.67,0:23:09.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,通知響個不停
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.29,0:23:12.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,把通知關掉比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.67,0:23:14.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,今後還會更多的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.82,0:23:16.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一萬 十萬
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.30,0:23:18.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,超越漢王朝的建國功臣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.35,0:23:22.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,率領百萬大軍的韓信大將軍也不是夢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.22,0:23:26.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,雖然我還是不懂你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.16,0:23:28.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不過這也是多虧了孔明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.39,0:23:31.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,難道說孔明其實很厲害？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.22,0:23:33.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,現在只是一介漂泊之人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.33,0:23:35.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就是個普通酒保
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.35,0:23:36.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,兼職工 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.90,0:23:38.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,話說我也一樣啊